title: Researchers Expose Deep Connections Between Maverick and Coyote Banking Malware

content.raw: Security researchers at CyberProof have uncovered critical connections between two sophisticated banking trojans Maverick and Coyote that are actively targeting Brazilian users through WhatsApp. The discovery came after investigating a suspicious file download incident flagged through the messaging platform, leading to a comprehensive threat analysis that reveals alarming similarities between the two malware families.
